{
  "stem": "26111.6",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I've put notice into, into their newsletter.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I've been sent a copy, a, a, a photo, in fact, of someone that may have known her, which, of course-- but when I saw the photo, I realized that she wasn't any of the four girls that were on the-- on the photo.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were-- they may be of some interest-- the-- which, to illustrate the limits on the freedom of movement of Jews in Berlin at that time, and I'm sure in other places in Germany.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Jews were allowed-- were not allowed to use public transportation, except on those routes which they had specific and written permission for on their person, which they had to show.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I have such a permit for my father, which was in the effects that I just described, which shows me the format.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it gives him permission to go-- to make multiple journeys.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It doesn't say per day.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But it's renewable annually.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So it seems as if the number of trips was not-- was not limited, not on this paper anyway, between his residence, which was on the outskirts of, of Berlin and the inner city of Berlin.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So that's all I know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My sister, apparently-- now I understood, once I had that paper, I understood better what happened to my sister, which I had until then, not quite understood because I didn't know the nature of this document.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She was working-- it was forced labor-- in a place somewhere in a Berlin suburb.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I think it was a Siemens.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I was told it was a Siemens subsidiary, the big electric company Siemens, which still exists.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And she was-- she had a permit, same as my father.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
